title: Suspicious object found in Red Fort, fire tenders reached spot
text:
Suspicious object found in Red Fort, fire tenders reached spot Suspicious object found in Red Fort, fire tenders reached spot A Suspicious object has been found inside Red Fort. By: FE Online | New Delhi | Updated: February 6, 2017 10:10 AM Red Fort in Delhi. Source: Reuters 
A suspicious object has been found inside Red Fort, fire tenders have reached the spot to inspect the suspected. 
Earlier today, Delhi police nabbed criminal Akbar who was carrying a reward of Rs 25000 on his head. Police was able to catch the criminal after a shootout between both the parties took place near Nehru Place metro. Whlie Akbar was nabbed, his aide managed to escape. 
(Further Details Awaited)
